{"about_the_game":"<strong>Blood Bay: Card History</strong> \u2013 This is a fairy tale ballad in the genre of card games.<br><br>In ancient times, when dragons burned villages, and pirates - ships ... When unconquered magic wandered the earth and the life of every person hung by a thread ... There was at that time a kingdom called the Archipelago, because it stood on a handful of islands in the Shark Sea . Difficult times overtook the kingdom after the death of the king: wars, famines, illnesses... The young, excited prince decided to put an end to this and went to the northern lands shrouded in mystery in search of treasures. And he happened to meet a demon there and he concluded a contract with him. Now the life of the kingdom depended only on him...<br><br><strong>Walk the path of the prince by choosing options for action!</strong><br><br><strong>Peculiarities:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You have to make a wise (and sometimes not very) choice that will determine the fate of the kingdom!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Colorful 2D graphics, hundreds of different cards!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Card narration of the plot and story!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851690/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734347791","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851690/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734347791","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851690/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734347791","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851690/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734347791","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<strong>Blood Bay: Card History</strong> \u2013 This is a fairy tale ballad in the genre of card games.<br><br>In ancient times, whe